title: SUMMER Slam Jam
body_text:
A new generation of
East Coast Dodgeball
battlers continues on their march towards greatness. This next encounter features a pair of the game's most talented female warriors when an all-star novice captain goes toe-to-toe with the most recognized lady veteran ever.
This is "Rookie vs. Legend: The Sequel."
With a successful collegiate softball career to her name,
Kelly Oberto
presently prepares to embrace the coveted, yet unfamiliar
ECD
spotlight. This no-nonsense, tough-as-nails, top-ranked competitor carries a plethora of athletic attributes and will utilize such strengths to her advantage at
SUMMER JAMBOREE
.
Born November 8, 1986
Debut December 29, 2007 | DODGEBALL 119
There is only one "first lady of dodgeball" and she is
Diana DiBuccio
. Over 170 appearances, a multiple-time event headliner, this loud-mouthed legend hasn't ceased fire just yet. Her nearly six years of wisdom and experience may grant her the slight edge heading into her July 16th showdown.
Born June 14, 1984
Debut September 3, 2005 | DODGEBALL DAY 1
The caliber of the captaincy occupants, the enormity of the encounter, all in one summer spectacular.
East Coast Dodgeball
presents
SUMMER JAMBOREE
on
July 16
at
5pm
only at
Wall High School
!

A new generation of East Coast Dodgeball battlers continues on their march towards greatness. This next encounter features a pair of the game's most talented female warriors when an all-star novice captain goes toe-to-toe with the most recognized lady veteran ever.

This is "Rookie vs. Legend: The Sequel."



With a successful collegiate softball career to her name, Kelly Oberto presently prepares to embrace the coveted, yet unfamiliar ECD spotlight. This no-nonsense, tough-as-nails, top-ranked competitor carries a plethora of athletic attributes and will utilize such strengths to her advantage at SUMMER JAMBOREE.
  • Born November 8, 1986
  • Debut December 29, 2007 | DODGEBALL 119

    There is only one "first lady of dodgeball" and she is Diana DiBuccio. Over 170 appearances, a multiple-time event headliner, this loud-mouthed legend hasn't ceased fire just yet. Her nearly six years of wisdom and experience may grant her the slight edge heading into her July 16th showdown.
  • Born June 14, 1984
  • Debut September 3, 2005 | DODGEBALL DAY 1

    The caliber of the captaincy occupants, the enormity of the encounter, all in one summer spectacular.
    East Coast Dodgeball presents SUMMER JAMBOREE on July 16 at 5pm only at Wall High School!
